|-------|---------------|-------------|
| Salary scale/notch calculation | calc | Given scale notation, compute annual/monthly salary for year N |
| Gross wage calculation | calc | Normal hours × rate + overtime hours × OT rate |
| Net salary/wage calculation | calc | Gross – (PAYE + pension + medical + UIF) |
| Salary/Wage journal completion | table | Fill employee rows: gross, deductions, net, employer contributions |
| Cost-to-company calculation | calc | Gross + all employer contributions |
| General ledger posting | table | Post journal totals to T-accounts (creditors, SARS-PAYE, pension, etc.) |
| CPJ completion | table | Cash payments journal with sundry accounts |
| Debit/credit identification | mcq/typed | Which account debited/credited for a given transaction |
| Accounting equation effect | mcq | A/E/L classification per wages/salary entry |
| Bonus/13th cheque calculation | calc | Monthly salary × bonus % |
| Ethics & internal control | typed | Internal control procedures for cash received |
| SDL calculation | calc | 1% of gross salaries/wages |

